# mlbz-nudge
> Simple dependency free ES6 library to produce small on-screen nudges

It simply allows you to display a small unobtrusive on-screen prompt for a few moments, very useful for saving notifications, new friend requests, updated messages etc.

![Demo](https://github.com/owenmelbz/mlbz-nudge/raw/master/demo.gif)
